data.description: Welcome to this charming traditional-style home, perfectly situated in the heart of Baton Rouge, in the highly sought-after Greenbriar Hollow subdivision, nestled between Bluebonnet and Siegen on Perkins Road. This well-maintained and updated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem offers the ideal blend of comfort and convenience, making it an exceptional place to call home. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the timeless elegance of wood floors that gracefully flow throughout all rooms. The bathrooms feature stylish ceramic tile, providing both durability and a touch of modern flair. Custom light fixtures and ceiling fans adorn the home, offering a delightful ambiance that complements every living space. The primary bedroom boasts an en suite bathroom with a separate stand-up shower and spacious walk-in closets, providing a private sanctuary for relaxation. Step outside to discover a fully enclosed backyard, complete with an electric gate for added security and convenience. Newer double-insulated, energy-efficient windows ensure that your home remains comfortable year-round, while also helping you save on energy costs. An additional open private courtyard offers a great spot for outdoor gatherings, and there's even an exterior storage room for all your tools and belongings. The exterior of the property is beautifully landscaped, creating an inviting and picturesque setting for your everyday life. Your peace of mind is further enhanced by the security cameras at the main entrance of the neighborhood. One of the standout features of this fantastic location is its proximity to key amenities. You're just minutes away from the Baton Rouge Mid-City hospital district, the Mall of Louisiana, and easy access to the interstate, making your daily commutes and shopping adventures a breeze.
